  11 Sep 2005; Steve Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org> lapack-atlas-3.6.0.ebuild:
  stable bump (sparc and x86) required for other sc-libs (besides, that
  configure bug doesn't really count, and the other one is *old*...)

